Pre-Game Insights: Kenya's strong start in qualifiers boosts hopes for AFCON return after missing out in 2023.
Cameroon has a talented squad but inconsistent recent performances.
Kenya has managed just one draw in their last three AFCON qualifiers against Cameroon.
Cameroon has never lost to Kenya in their eight previous meetings.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match is crucial as Kenya aims to secure a spot in AFCON 2025.
The Harambee Stars are forced to play their home matches in Kampala due to a lack of FIFA and CAF-approved stadiums in Kenya.
